<i>In shocking news,</i>

1586
01:31:33,618 --> 01:31:36,403
<i>business tycoon King Kwang
has been arrested</i>

1587
01:31:36,403 --> 01:31:38,623
<i>for illegal possession
of firearms in Taiwan.</i>

1588
01:31:38,623 --> 01:31:41,844
<i>Which has some of the toughest
gun-control law in the world...</i>

1589
01:31:41,844 --> 01:31:43,106
