Instead, you went rogue.</i>

1601
01:32:16,835 --> 01:32:18,402
<i>You couldn't
even bring the ledger.</i>

1602
01:32:18,402 --> 01:32:20,535
Yeah, well, I got
something better.

1603
01:32:20,535 --> 01:32:23,233
