shipping manifests,

1604
01:32:23,233 --> 01:32:26,018
supplies, buyers,
illegal carbon offsets.

1605
01:32:26,018 --> 01:32:27,672
<i>- This is real.</i>
- More than real.

1606
01:32:27,672 --> 01:32:29,195
<i>Okay, let me handle
it from here.</i>

1607
01:32:29,195 --> 01:32:31,981
<i>Until then,
you better disappear.</i>

1608
01:32:31,981 --> 01:32:33,939
<i>For real this time.</i>

1609
01:32:34,244 --> 01:32:36,376
<i>- Vanish. All of you.</i>
- For the weekend?

1610
01:32:36,376 --> 01:32:38,030
<i>Make it a couple of weeks...</i>

1611
01:32:38,030 --> 01:32:39,902
<i>couple of years.</i>

1612
01:32:43,296 --> 01:32:45,124
